gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 128, Thunder 123
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Thunder, 128-123. DeAaron Fox led the Kings with 41 points, seven assists, and five 3PT FG as Malik Monk (18 points, nine assists) and Domantas Sabonis (18 points, 16 rebounds, seven assists) totaled 36 points. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander tallied his fourth 40-point game of the year with 43 points, six rebounds, and nine assists as Chet Holmgren added 14 points and 10 rebounds. The Kings improve to 14-9 as the Thunder move to 15-8.
